# ASAuthorizationWebBrowserPublicKeyCredentialManager.AuthorizationState.notDetermined

**Case**

The person has yet to choose whether to allow the browser app to access passkeys stored on the keychain, or managed by third-party credential managers.

## Declaration

```swift
case notDetermined
```

## Passkey access states

- **ASAuthorizationWebBrowserPublicKeyCredentialManager.AuthorizationState.authorized**: Someone allows the browser app to use passkeys stored in the keychain, and managed by third-party credential manager apps.
- **ASAuthorizationWebBrowserPublicKeyCredentialManager.AuthorizationState.denied**: Someone forbids the browser app to use passkeys stored in the keychain, and managed by third-party credential manager apps.
